   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Multilingual Sentiment Analysis\\n\",\"**NLP Project 62 of 100** — Perform sentiment analysis across multiple languages using multilingual transformers.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Use multilingual models (XLM-RoBERTa) for cross-lingual sentiment.\\n\",\"2. Compare single-language vs multilingual approaches.\\n\",\"3. Evaluate on multiple languages.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import subprocess, sys, importlib\\nfor pkg in ['pandas','numpy','matplotlib','seaborn','transformers','torch']:\\n    try: importlib.import_module(pkg)\\n    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,'-m','pip','install','-q',pkg])\\nprint('Ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nSEED = 42\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Multilingual test sentences\\ntest_data = [\\n    {'text':'I love this product, it is amazing!','lang':'English','expected':'positive'},\\n    {'text':'This is terrible, worst purchase ever.','lang':'English','expected':'negative'},\\n    {'text':'Me encanta este producto, es increíble!','lang':'Spanish','expected':'positive'},\\n    {'text':'Esto es terrible, la peor compra.','lang':'Spanish','expected':'negative'},\\n    {'text':'J\\\\'adore ce produit, c\\\\'est incroyable!','lang':'French','expected':'positive'},\\n    {'text':'C\\\\'est terrible, le pire achat jamais fait.','lang':'French','expected':'negative'},\\n    {'text':'Ich liebe dieses Produkt, es ist erstaunlich!','lang':'German','expected':'positive'},\\n    {'text':'Das ist schrecklich, der schlechteste Kauf.','lang':'German','expected':'negative'},\\n]\\ndf = pd.DataFrame(test_data)\\nprint(f'Test samples: {len(df)} across {df[\\\"lang\\\"].nunique()} languages')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Multilingual Sentiment with Pipeline\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"from transformers import pipeline\\nimport torch\\n\\ndevice = 0 if torch.cuda.is_available() else -1\\nsentiment_pipe = pipeline('sentiment-analysis', model='nlptown/bert-base-multilingual-uncased-sentiment', device=device)\\n\\nresults = []\\nfor _, row in df.iterrows():\\n    pred = sentiment_pipe(row['text'][:512])[0]\\n    stars = int(pred['label'][0])  # '1 star' to '5 stars'\\n    sentiment = 'positive' if stars >= 4 else ('negative' if stars <= 2 else 'neutral')\\n    results.append({'text': row['text'][:50], 'lang': row['lang'], 'expected': row['expected'],\\n                    'predicted': sentiment, 'stars': stars, 'confidence': round(pred['score'], 3)})\\n\\nresults_df = pd.DataFrame(results)\\nprint(results_df.to_string(index=False))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"accuracy = (results_df['expected'] == results_df['predicted']).mean()\\nprint(f'\\\\nOverall accuracy: {accuracy:.1%}')\\n\\n# Per-language accuracy\\nfor lang in results_df['lang'].unique():\\n    mask = results_df['lang'] == lang\\n    acc = (results_df.loc[mask,'expected'] == results_df.loc[mask,'predicted']).mean()\\n    print(f'  {lang}: {acc:.1%}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,4))\\nresults_df.groupby('lang').apply(lambda x: (x['expected']==x['predicted']).mean()).plot(kind='bar', ax=ax, color='steelblue')\\nax.set_title('Accuracy by Language'); ax.set_ylim(0,1.1); ax.set_ylabel('Accuracy')\\nplt.tight_layout(); plt.show()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Multilingual transformer models handle sentiment across languages** without separate models.\\n\",\"- **Performance is generally consistent** across major European languages.\\n\",\"- **For low-resource languages, accuracy may drop significantly.**\\n\",\"- **For production, fine-tune on domain-specific multilingual data.**\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
